  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f39870d683ef5dc27d3b319ae63401a1.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play online with up to 16 players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/4a0c9d4ee4723b916d7138bd6e6ffbce.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Anything can be a weapon, cause maximum carnage and throw everything!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/764a49a7b1aa2d7447706853f994f80e.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>A variety of chaotic game modes to fight through, and we’ll keep adding more maps, game modes and rewards!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/2d6f30c72fac5dc715741335b295126b.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Do damage, build rage and your character will get huge! Your character is customisable and there are a bunch of character skins waiting to be unlocked!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN THE BRAWL AND ENTER A FANTASTIC FESTIVAL OF FIGHTING! GET MAD, GET BIG, GET EVEN!</h2><br>Wishlist now to stay up-to-date with the latest development updates and be the first to know when OutRage: Fight Fest releases. Join our  community and get access to exclusive beta play sessions where you can help shape the game.<br><br>If you're looking for the Physics-Based interactions of Party Animals but want more depth and bigger fights, or if you want the multiplayer madness of Stumble Guys, then OutRage: Fight Fest is the game for you!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f39870d683ef5dc27d3b319ae63401a1.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Play online with up to 16 players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/4a0c9d4ee4723b916d7138bd6e6ffbce.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Anything can be a weapon, cause maximum carnage and throw everything!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/764a49a7b1aa2d7447706853f994f80e.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>A variety of chaotic game modes to fight through, and we’ll keep adding more maps, game modes and rewards!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/2d6f30c72fac5dc715741335b295126b.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Do damage, build rage and your character will get huge! Your character is customisable and there are a bunch of character skins waiting to be unlocked!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN THE BRAWL AND ENTER A FANTASTIC FESTIVAL OF FIGHTING! GET MAD, GET BIG, GET EVEN!</h2><br>Wishlist now to stay up-to-date with the latest development updates and be the first to know when OutRage: Fight Fest releases. Join our  community and get access to exclusive beta play sessions where you can help shape the game.<br><br>If you're looking for the Physics-Based interactions of Party Animals but want more depth and bigger fights, or if you want the multiplayer madness of Stumble Guys, then OutRage: Fight Fest is the game for you!",
